The V-51 resolved resonance parameter evaluation was done in      2328 1451
the energy range from 1e-5 eV to 200 keV with the SAMMY [ref1].   2328 1451
Capture and transmission measurements were part of the evaluation.2328 1451
The experimental data used in the evaluation were those carried   2328 1451
at the GELINA LINAC [ref2] done by K. Guber.[ref3]                2328 1451
 Thermal cross section [ref4,5] data available in the EXFOR       2328 1451
library were also used in the evaluation.                         2328 1451
                                                                  2328 1451
 Resonance parameter covariance matrices were also obtained in    2328 1451
the SAMMY evaluation process in the energy region 1e-5 eV-200 keV.2328 1451
The RML formalism (LRF=7) was used for the resonance parameters   2328 1451
and the compact formalism (LCOMP=2) for the covariance matrix.    2328 1451
